{"tid":616761,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想入手XT20同一支定焦鏡","createTime":"2018-04-04T12:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T15:22:12.000Z","uid":85056,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"730bdd8e2d2c862f771825cdfd3afa6efc08736b","tid":616761,"uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"各位連登高手<br />\n小弟新手用開普通機仔好多年<br />\n呢兩年成日要幫女友影瑜伽相<br />\n發現影黎影去都唔夠好FEEL<br />\n除左技術唔夠呢樣我知之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係人像影得唔夠出<br />\n做左陣功課想入手XT20無反 (單反太重唔考慮了)<br />\n新手睇左陣D SPEC, 見原裝鏡係18-55mm, 光圈2.8<br />\n唔知夠唔夠影到咁 (距離差唔多):<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/200445_92abaa487639ec10bb8c365d0539219b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F200445_92abaa487639ec10bb8c365d0539219b.jpg&h=c258922d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/200445_83a09fd2f334c27c603eab6fd4ef6859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F200445_83a09fd2f334c27c603eab6fd4ef6859.jpg&h=365cd0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/200445_b241085cd19795218fdaa0deeb3d4214.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F04%2F200445_b241085cd19795218fdaa0deeb3d4214.jpg&h=bf0fa281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以想考慮另外買支大光圈既定焦鏡,<br />\n上富士個網睇到有呢幾支:<br />\nXF23mmF1.4 R<br />\nXF35mmF1.4 R<br />\nXF56mmF1.2 R<br />\n<br />\n小弟真係全新手, 都係一個鐘前上網睇過下鏡頭D spec係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想請教下如果想影到上面咁, 原裝鏡夠唔夠做, 定要買多支定焦鏡 (咩spec好)?<br />\n謝謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccb4f0e8769aa64f714b1428c248867901dde7bd","tid":616761,"uid":15257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"XT20 + 56.2"},{"pid":"5c7e17b1f8c3cd27053c2cf2a09780759f47d969","tid":616761,"uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ccb4f0e8769aa64f714b1428c248867901dde7bd","tid":616761,"uid":15257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"XT20 + 56.2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"thanks!<br />\n其實睇左少少焦距係乜<br />\n知道數字愈大可以影既就愈遠<br />\n但又會因為唔同機要乘返倍數<br />\n所以我唔知實際我要點預<br />\n因為我理解定焦鏡要自己就個距離<br />\n想知55mm, 我同被影者相距2米影唔影到全身?"},{"pid":"2c0400eeecb0c2505e6a3e54899e468ca2ce91cc","tid":616761,"uid":40445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c7e17b1f8c3cd27053c2cf2a09780759f47d969","tid":616761,"uid":85056,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ccb4f0e8769aa64f714b1428c248867901dde7bd","tid":616761,"uid":15257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"XT20 + 56.2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"thanks!<br />\n其實睇左少少焦距係乜<br />\n知道數字愈大可以影既就愈遠<br />\n但又會因為唔同機要乘返倍數<br />\n所以我唔知實際我要點預<br />\n因為我理解定焦鏡要自己就個距離<br />\n想知55mm, 我同被影者相距2米影唔影到全身?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"巴打，你可以試下用呢個網<br />\nXT20+56 1.2 太約要6米先影到一個1.6米高女仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://dofsimulator.net/en/?x=EIwAYWLuAAAIM0wkAAADhpf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdofsimulator.net%2Fen%2F%3Fx%3DEIwAYWLuAAAIM0wkAAADhpf&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2Btb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=74c85a75\" target=\"_blank\">https://dofsimulator.net/en/?x=EIwAYWLuAAAIM0wkAAADhpf</a><br />\n<br />\n兩米要影到全身，都算幾廣角嘅鏡頭<br />\n如果XT20+23mm，2米幾影到全身<br />\n<a href=\"https://dofsimulator.net/en/?x=EDmAoWEjIAAIM0wkAAADhsE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdofsimulator.net%2Fen%2F%3Fx%3DEDmAoWEjIAAIM0wkAAADhsE&d=M%2BVLkElJh%2F0an4e%2F%2B3q%2Btb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=8ae575ce\" target=\"_blank\">h